defmodule Solution do
  @spec beautiful_indices(s :: String.t, a :: String.t, b :: String.t, k :: integer) :: [integer]
  def beautiful_indices(s, a, b, k) do
    Enum.filter(0..(String.length(s) - String.length(a)), fn i ->
      String.slice(s, i, String.length(a)) == a &&
      Enum.any?(0..(String.length(s) - String.length(b)), fn j ->
        String.slice(s, j, String.length(b)) == b && abs(j - i) <= k
      end)
    end)
  end
end
